
### Case Panel
Shows the list of the investigated pcap files.
![[Pasted image 20240604100813.png]]


### Hosts
The "hosts" menu shows the identified hosts in the pcap file. This section provides information on;

- IP address
- MAC address
- OS type
- Open ports
- Sent/Received packets
- Incoming/Outgoing sessions
- Host details

### Sessions
The "hosts" menu shows the identified hosts in the pcap file. This section provides information on;

- IP address
- MAC address
- OS type
- Open ports
- Sent/Received packets
- Incoming/Outgoing sessions
- Host details

### DNS
The DNS menu shows DNS queries with details. This section provides information on;

- Frame number
- Timestamp
- Client and server
- Source and destination port 
- IP TTL
- DNS time
- Transaction ID and type
- DNS query and answer
- Alexa Top 1M


### **Credentials**
 - Kerberos hashes
- NTLM hashes
- RDP cookies
- HTTP cookies  
- HTTP requests
- IMAP
- FTP
- SMTP
- MS SQL
